Package org.apache.ignite.spi.collision

Interface CollisionExternalListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EventListener
    public interface CollisionExternalListener
extends EventListener
    Listener to be set on CollisionSpi for notification of external collision events (e.g. job stealing). Once grid receives such notification, it will immediately invoke collision SPI.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method Description
      void onExternalCollision()
      Callback invoked by Collision SPI whenever an external collision event occurs.
